 /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1819e6d9dee38e825d07caa42306208c40a1d218","tid":1200644,"uid":69000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d6db7ddb33a3140bbec7a1e2000a38367cb8781a","tid":1200644,"uid":64053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17f36d611dbdfd318f3bf573c6169e026078c780","tid":1200644,"uid":69000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:50:10.000Z","msg":"有我母校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:52:08.000Z","msg":"簽左未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T21:53:58.000Z","msg":"啱啱簽咗"},{"pid":"c9302a9addbd61a3ba93f16b0987c746a847d418","tid":1200644,"uid":64053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:03:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"763e95a968cfc7d28bc8a8d2525b0ab02d285650","tid":1200644,"uid":139704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:09:18.000Z","msg":"Proud of the young generation"},{"pid":"9176a6b99237730af456b08f6166f5cca94457dd","tid":1200644,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:10:28.000Z","msg":"[AUS/PMP2018]大學生輔警(狗)計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/933751\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/933751</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n成班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15a90ee1115fd65fb474bd339eb79229d9f2e05","tid":1200644,"uid":241310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NifzLR3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNifzLR3.jpg&h=5e78dfc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以嘅話晒你幾秒鐘，入去留個言，可以嘅話叫多啲朋友來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n〔置頂〕唔通溫和派就無嘢可以做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1199622/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1199622/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟通知咗大家我聽日會去同朋友拎錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果順路可以join埋，<strong>中環所有銀行</strong>都有總行，你拎港紙／美金都無所謂，甚至問開戶詳情都得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最鍾意<strong>多人喺中環</strong>來睇我拎錢，你唔撳都可以來睇<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好問有無用</span><br />\n<br />\n利申：非鍵戰，就算聽日得我同朋友同記者都照去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n我哩個係新自發嘅行動，想畀更多人知道<br />\n哩個活動十分低成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係需要你排一排隊，去撳錢；<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果多人，甚至可能撳唔到錢</span></strong><br />\n適合有包袱，又想做嘢嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<strong>散播虛假消息係犯法</strong>，唔好為咗更多人來睇「我」撳錢，就去作料！<br />\n已經搵咗記者朋友，歡迎大家繼續share出去！<br />\n同時唔好煽動其他人！其他人陣間見到都去撳錢就&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n可能有人唔認同，覺得我做嘅杯水車薪，但唔做過又點知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b48951157f61cb1237379ccdfe908efa666264","tid":1200644,"uid":102698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:19:07.000Z","msg":"而家呢段考試時間罷課真係有啲尷尬<br />\n倘若間學校本身有立場嘅話<br />\n見你罷課一個屈尾十直0咗你嗰科<br />\n學生都未必肯<br />\n<br />\n尤其而家咁多親中學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52c885b8dde3ad51199ebdf79a28f385fb70455","tid":1200644,"uid":139176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:59:21.000Z","msg":"我都學校唔會比到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca3092efd58461cdc1e41dc54667e2d6ea9167f","tid":1200644,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T22:59:42.000Z","msg":"車既手足 唔該幫幫手 塞一塞住條路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1194860\" target=\"_blank\">https:/